You can use iTunes File Sharing Feature to transfer music and video from you iPhone or iPad to your computer  
1. [Use iTunes File Sharing Feature](https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201301)  
2. [A video sample for iTunes File Sharing Feature on Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XC0jAGTPxb8)
